      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KUNG FU ETHICS (1) was in the minors two back (19.46) at Bulli but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Tough to beat if on-song. EXCITING FORTE (2) is a first starter from the Simon Gafa kennel by Craigie Delegate out of Dubrovnik. Drawn well and should get her chance. Profiles strongly for this and can make an immediate impact. ZIPPING AMOS (7) turned in a plain performance last time when seventh at The Gardens over 400m behind Goldilocks Gort (24.93) in a Maiden. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. EXQUISITE ETHICS (3) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.",
